                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 16.904,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 96381,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in Miller-El versus Dretke and the opinion of the Court in Grable \u0026 Sons Metal Products versus Darue Engineering will both be announced by Justice Souter."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 16.904,
